charts.description:
The chart will shows data completeness and timeliness by orgunit for the last quarter. 
The completeness and timeliness indicators should be used to monitor performance and assess the validity of the data prior to analysis.

charts.name: HIV: HIV cascade by gender - last 12 months
charts.description:
HIV positive tests, PLHIV newly on ART and PLHIV retained on treatment over the past 12 months by gender.
For monitoring HIV programme effectiveness for test and treat policy and retention on treatment over time by gender.

charts.name: HIV: HIV retention and viral load suppression rates - last 12 months

PLHIV retention rate (%) and virological suppression rate (%) by month in past 12 months.
For tracking trends in sustaining ART over time.
